{"word":"G2647 - καταλύω - katalýō - kat-al-oo'-o - Destroy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταλύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katalýō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-al-oo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Destroy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழி, இடி"},{"paragraph":"to dissolve, disunite"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G3089 - λύω - lýō - loo'-o/3089\">G3089</a>; to <i>loosen down</i> (<i>disintegrate</i>), that is, (by implication) to <i>demolish</i> (literally or figuratively); specifically (compare <a href=\"#/G2646 - κατάλυμα - katályma - kat-al'-oo-mah/2646\">G2646</a>) to <i>halt</i> for the night: - destroy, dissolve, be guest, lodge, come to nought, overthrow, throw down.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G179/179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955/1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G1956/1956\">G1956</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646/2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G2647/2647\">G2647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083/3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084/3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085/3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086/3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089/3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359/359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360/360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487/487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G629/629\">G629</a>, <a href=\"#/G630/630\">G630</a>"}]}